 Damilola Mike-Bamiloye has released the teaser for the forthcoming movie “Heart Pain“, showing on Sunday 2nd of May. The movie follows the story of two parents seeking a solution for their daughter, who seems possessed by the spirit of a character from a movie she watches. “Heart Pain” is written and produced by Mike Bamiloye. Watch the teaser below:   The best Nigerian and African video content from around the web specially curated for YOU! 